{
  "stem": "935.2",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I left Vienna exactly the day the Nazis much into Austria.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I crossed the border into Switzerland the day the Nazis marched in.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It had nothing to do with foresight.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I had not a clue, of course not.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Except I never came back.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I left for six weeks and came back for the first time only because my mother was still alive, 26 years later.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So that's, that's when it started to be aware.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And, again, I wasn't really aware or did understand.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I did not understand.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I celebrated success.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "I had fantastic critics.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "I had fantastic success.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And it's all I celebrated, except I should've known.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "In my passport at that time, it was customary to have your religion.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "It was called Mosaic Jewish.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "I don't think that exists anymore.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "But you had your religion.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And my indicator should have been short-term visas-- entered, left, entered, left, entered, left.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "I had become a gypsy.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "I went from one country to the other, wherever they would let me in, work, stay a while, go onto the next, work.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "I spent a lot of time in crummy little offices in police stations-- not because I was arrested, but asking for a visa, permission to work, permission to stay another week, another week, another week.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And, actually, for two years, I was always a bit ahead of the Nazis.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "Again, had nothing to do with foresight.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "It just happened that way.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "I remember, I had a contract in Czechoslovakia, had laryngitis, had to cancel.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "So I was in another country just that the Germans marched into Czechoslovakia.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "When Poland was crushed, I went from one country to the other, always ahead of the Nazis.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "I wasn't running away from them.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "It just happened that way.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, I knew.",
      "word_count": 3
    }
  ],
